turalsInduction_proofs.tla:<1>1. ASSUME NEW i \\in Nat, NEW g, NEW h,\n/home/ubuntu/.tlapm/lib/tlapm/stdlib/NaturalsInduction_proofs.tla:<1>3. ASSUME NEW i \\in Nat, P(i)\n/home/ubuntu/.tlapm/lib/tlapm/stdlib/NaturalsInduction_proofs.tla:<1>3. ASSUME NEW i \\in Nat, P(i)\n/home/ubuntu/.tlapm/lib/tlapm/stdlib/NaturalsInduction_proofs.tla:<1>2. QED\n/home/ubuntu/.tlapm/lib/tlapm/stdlib/NaturalsInduction_proofs.tla:<1>2. QED\n/home/ubuntu/.tlapm/lib/tlapm/stdlib/NaturalsInduction.tla:<1>2. QED\n/home/ubuntu/.tlapm/lib/tlapm/stdlib/NaturalsInduction.tla:<1>2. QED\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
